title: Fausto 5.0 (2001)
description:
Dr. Fausto is a hard-working, eminent oncologist who's haunted by thoughts of death. Traveling to a medical convention, he runs into a man who claims the doctor removed his stomach eight years ago in a surgical operation. Although Dr. Fausto has no recall of this, the extremely resourceful stranger seems intent on doing him a few favors. Can the good doctor resist temptation?
